int. From these results, it can be concluded\nthat those $f(R)$ models allow such phase transitions of the universe to\nrealize the late-time accelerated expansion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Dec 2022 06:39:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
