ed model is implemented\nusing an efficient MCMC algorithm that permits rigorous full Bayesian inference\nat a scale that is orders of magnitude beyond the capability of out-of-the-box\nhigh-dimensional multi-class regression methods and software. We employ our\nmodel on the Pan Cancer Analysis of Whole Genomes (PCAWG) dataset, and our\nresults reveal interesting novel insights.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Dec 2022 06:47:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
